body:
Hello Summoners,

I am one of your wonderful team at University of Wollongong's Video Game Association. 
We are happy to help and support another season of university games. 
Can't wait to see how we go and have fun playing some intense matches.

Swing by https://www.facebook.com/groups/LoLVGA/ for all our LOL group chat

 https://www.facebook.com/UowVGA 

Use this thread for all your UOW talk as well

Regards,

Drew
